data.description: This beautiful open concept home is newly renovated, including roof, siding, all electrical, plumbing and natural gas systems. As well as furnace, AC, all ductwork, hot water heater, insulation, windows, doors, flooring, walls, shutters and hard wired smoke detectors. Beautiful natural gas fireplace,MA beautiful colonial home located close to shopping, dining and Lake St. Clair!  This 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath offers newer flooring, remodeled kitchen, remodeled bathrooms and a master bedroom that includes a walk in natural light closet.  The property has a finished basement, detached garage on large lot with fenced in backyard 480 sq. ft. This home is a must see! Master closet is approximately 140 sq. ft. with it's own window and could be used as a nursery.
